{
  "stem": "27507.8",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was this area of maybe two streets surrounded by barbed wire, with their own factory guard, police, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[POLISH], that means that was guard of the factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not anymore Jewish police, necessarily, maybe they were Jewish as well, but they were only belonging to the factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you couldn't go in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you couldn't go out without the permission.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that wasn't-- you know that in Israel-- you know what [NON-ENGLISH] means?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so on, so that expression, soap, I already remember it from '42.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But one didn't know, I think, in '42 still during the action all the details.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people did, because some people came even back from Treblinka, but few.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in '42 after the action, then it slowly, everybody started-- it was found out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was more and more people knew about more and more details.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were some people who escaped from Treblinka, and from transports, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it became obvious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then people started digging bunkers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Building--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were bunkers everywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They started building bunkers deep into the ground, and putting-- the building them properly, with bricks, and with concrete, and with furniture, putting bunk beds into them, and connecting them to water supply, and to electricity supply, and-- and to canalization, to the drainage system, so that some of those bunkers were really brilliant.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of the bunkers were well excellently built, and excellently equipped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And many people lived in them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Many, many people lived in those bunkers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, of course, nobody realized that what was this area of big houses, and big blocks of houses, and huge-- which was still intact at this time, was still there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The houses were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The people were not there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
